	<h2>Overture Users</h2>
	<p>If you wish to be added to this list, please&nbsp;<a style="color: rgb(51,102,153); text-decoration: none" href="http://www.google.com/recaptcha/mailhide/d?k=01mU5bAq4Rogp5FVouKumLoQ==&amp;c=pHoefT8t8vvgTnqYB_4422-4CEytwUaijr_er5aSbIw=">send us a mail</a>. You can also enter a mailing list for Overture users:</p>
	<p>This mailing list is the main channel of communication of the <b>user</b> comunity.</p>
	<p>To post a message to this mailing list, send a mail to <a title="mailto:overture-users@overturetool.org" class="external text" href="mailto:overture-users@overturetool.org" rel="nofollow"><u><font color="#0066cc">overture-users@overturetool.org</font></u></a></p>
	<p>To see the mailing list archives go to <a title="http://overturetool.hosting.west.nl/mailman/private/overture-users/" class="external text" href="http://overturetool.hosting.west.nl/mailman/private/overture-users/" rel="nofollow"><u><font color="#0066cc">Overture-Users archives</font></u></a>.</p>
	<p>To subscribe to this mailing list please fill the <a title="http://overturetool.hosting.west.nl/mailman/listinfo/overture-users" class="external text" href="http://overturetool.hosting.west.nl/mailman/listinfo/overture-users" rel="nofollow"><u><font color="#0066cc">subscription form</font></u></a>.</p>
